                        <interp inst="t18420404-name-708" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY FLETCHER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a bookseller, in Clerkenwell. On the 25th of February the prisoner came to my shop, and asked for a black lead pencil, which came to 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—he offered a bad half-crown in payment—I told him it was bad—he said he did not know it—I sent for a policeman, and gave him into custody, and gave the half-crown to the policeman.</p>
               <p>
